lyrics:
[verse]
Максим, little gnome, so small and bright
He wanders through the woods, day and night
With his pointy hat and his joyful smile
He spreads happiness, mile after mile

[chorus]
Oh, Максим, little gnome, a magical sight
Dancing through the meadows, under moonlight
With his shimmering lantern and his tiny feet
Максим, little gnome, brings joy complete
